resources.string: Deskargatu eta instalatu LED View Cover eginbide osagarriak. Zeure LED ikonoak sortu eta jakinarazpen ikono gisa ezar ditzakezu. Haiek geroago deskargatzeko, zoaz Ezarpenak > Eginbide aurreratuak > Osagarriak > LED View Cover atalera, eta hautatu Deskargatu eginbide osagarriak.

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
